import React from 'react'; const Comparables = ({ properties }) => { const comparableCount = properties.length; const averagePrice = comparableCount > 0 ? properties.reduce((sum, p) => sum + (p.price || 0), 0) / comparableCount : 0; const pricePerSqft = comparableCount > 0 ? properties.reduce((sum, p) => sum + ((p.price || 0) / (p.square_feet || 1)), 0) / comparableCount : 0; const formatPrice = (price) => { return new Intl.NumberFormat('en-GB', { style: 'currency', currency: 'GBP', minimumFractionDigits: 0, maximumFractionDigits: 0, }).format(price); }; return (

Comparable Properties

{comparableCount} properties found
{properties.length > 0 ? (
{properties.map((property) => (
{property.address}
{property.postcode}

Price:

Type:

Bedrooms:

Area:

Distance:

{formatPrice(property.price)}

{property.property_type || 'N/A'}

{property.bedrooms || 'N/A'}

{property.square_feet ? `${property.square_feet} sq ft` : 'N/A'}

{property.distance_to ? `${property.distance_to} miles` : 'N/A'}

Adjustments
  • Location: {property.location_adjustment ? `${property.location_adjustment.toFixed(1)}%` : 'N/A'}
  • Size: {property.size_adjustment ? `${property.size_adjustment.toFixed(1)}%` : 'N/A'}
  • Market: {property.market_adjustment ? `${property.market_adjustment.toFixed(1)}%` : 'N/A'}
Adjusted Value

{property.adjusted_value ? formatPrice(property.adjusted_value) : 'N/A'}

Days on Market: {property.days_on_market || 'N/A'}
))}
) : (
No comparable properties found.
Ask for comparables within your ideal distance from your subject property.
)}
); }; export default Comparables;
